BASL membership

Apply for membership at BSE Administration & Supervision Ltd (BASL) online (membership.bseasl.com). BASL membership is required before applying to SEBI. Prepare Form-A and supporting documents. 

Apply to SEBI for IA registration

Fill Form A (SEBI IA Regulations), submit documents, pay fees. Prepare required undertakings, client agreement templates, fee structure, deposit (as required by SEBI based on clients), and compliance manual.

