Fee structure & conflict rules

SEBI expects fee-only (or disclosure) and clear statements on commissions/conflicts. Publish fee schedule and client disclosures.

Operational controls

Logging, audit trails, encryption, secure storage. Keep client documents and risk profiling signed/emailed and archived.

