Register GST, collect & remit GST on Indian clients; for foreign clients follow “export of services” zero-rated rules (LUT/bond or IGST + refund). Consult CA for export compliance and refunds. 

Purchase Professional Indemnity (E&O) insurance

Strongly recommended for IA firms to cover claims of negligence. See Indian insurers offering E&O/PI for financial professionals. 

Ongoing compliance

Periodic reporting to BASL/SEBI, maintain minimum deposits (if applicable), grievance redressal email/contacts, internal compliance officer functions.

